'I see that you have gained proficiency as an expert woodworker! That is excellent, [placeholder]. You are showing remarkable progress.

'You are about ready to learn to be an artisan woodworker, which is the next step along your path to mastery. To do this, though, you will need to prove your worth to the expert woodworker in Esteldín.

'If you impress Tadhrien, she may allow you to use the superior workbench to carve sturdy tools and weapons from your artisan recipes. Not many have this honour!'
